	- hmmmmm - for floating point operation tips.
	https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=307755
	
======================================================================================
	
	Relationship:
	
	 - Command and ConVar - Buffer Overflow Fixer
	 https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=309656

======================================================================================*/

